node.text: A special birthday deserves a special present. With the extraordinary 911 GT2 RS Clubsport 25, Porsche Motorsport celebrates the 25th anniversary of Manthey-Racing in muscular style and considerable power. Bridging the gap between the two 911 generations, it’s a technology and aerodynamic masterclass. Designed for track days and circuit racing, and with inspiration from Manthey’s legendary ‘Grello’ 911 GT3 R, the 515kW/700PS is limited to just 30 examples.
